I had such a fun time with @thepinkfoundry and @mintandmilkpr in Goa! 💖🎀

Definitely a science backed brand to look out for! I’m the process of trying their products and can’t wait to share my thought on it! 💖💖

latestPosts.caption:
#GraziaBeauty Chapell Roan was the beauty icon in 2024 that we didn’t know we needed. With her rising drag-inspired make-up influence on the beauty community and runway’s love for bright, neon hues, colours took on a bold and subversive turn this year. This approach of using clashing bright hues not only broke the rules of make-up, but also served as a great way to express your creativity. Wearing colours might not be anything new, but Roan gve it a more modern and refreshing take.

Words: Konika Datta 
Photograph: Yusuf Lokhandwala
Make-up: Saikat Chakraborty, National Artist, M.A.C Cosmetics India
Hair: Shimchuila Mungkung (Ashim) and Nikesh Sharma, Looks Salon
